Wang Zhigang{{efn|Wang Zhigang's position is unusual in that he is a party branch secretary of a ministry, as opposed to a minister. In most cases, a minister is concurrently the party branch secretary of the ministry. In this case, the Minister of Science and Technology, [[Wan Gang]], is not a member of the Communist Party, so Wang tends to party duties at the ministry and is ranked as a full minister-level official.}}
